python-bottle (0.8.0-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * debian/patches/01-fix_quiet_parsing.patch added, thanks to Enrico
    Zini: only use "quiet" parameter inside run(), i.e. don't pass it
    to the server adapter (Closes: #584781)

